{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"title":"OUDSTag","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false,"name":"iOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"name":"macOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","name":"tvOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","name":"watchOS","beta":false}]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Appearances","anchor":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"emphasized","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary or high-priority information."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Status","anchor":"Status","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Neutral","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status needs to be communicated.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Accent","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Negative","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Info","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or contextual information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}]},{"text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allowed when loader is activated.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Shape","anchor":"Shape","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Square","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Size","anchor":"Size","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two sizes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Layout","anchor":"Layout"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There are four available layouts for tags:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Icon","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Loader"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anc